MyAspNetApp (Solution)
|
+---> Web/Api (ASP.NET Web and/or API)
|   |
|   +---> Business (To call IServices & acknowledge DIs)
|   |
|   +---> Data (To acknowledge DIs)
|   |
|   +---> Shared (To access shared helpers)
|	|
|	+---> Api.Models (To access api/view models)
|
+---> Business (Service/Business Logic Layer)
|   |
|   +---> Business.Abstraction (To implement Interfaces & setup DI)
|   |
|   +---> Data.Abstraction (To call IRepositories)
|   |
|   +---> Shared (To access shared helpers)
|
+---> Data (Repository/Data access Layer)
|   |
|   +---> Data.Abstraction (To implement Interfaces & setup DI)
|   |
|   +---> Shared (To access shared helpers)
|
+---> Business.Abstraction (Service/Business Logic Interfaces)
|   |
|   +---> Business.Models (To define return type as DTOs in IService methods)
|
+---> Data.Abstraction (Repository/Data access Interfaces)
|   |
|   +---> Data.Models (To define return type as Entities in IRepository methods)
|
+---> Api.Models (API/View Models)
|
+---> Business.Models (DTOs)
|
+---> Data.Models (Entities and Custom Data Types)
|
+---> Shared (Common Helpers)
